hwMeta.bodyText:
Switch(arAddr)\
    .Case(0,
        bus_r_data(decoded_id_reg_din))\
    .Case(4,
        bus_r_data(decoded_cmd_and_status_din))\
    .Case(8,
        bus_r_data(decoded_addr_din))\
    .Case(12,
        bus_r_data(Concat(Bits(26).from_py(0, 0), decoded_ar_aw_w_id_din)))\
    .Case(16,
        bus_r_data(Concat(Bits(30).from_py(0, 0), decoded_burst_din)))\
    .Case(20,
        bus_r_data(Concat(Bits(28).from_py(0, 0), decoded_cache_din)))\
    .Case(24,
        bus_r_data(Concat(Bits(24).from_py(0, 0), decoded_len_din)))\
    .Case(28,
        bus_r_data(Concat(Bits(31).from_py(0, 0), decoded_lock_din)))\
    .Case(32,
        bus_r_data(Concat(Bits(29).from_py(0, 0), decoded_prot_din)))\
    .Case(36,
        bus_r_data(Concat(Bits(29).from_py(0, 0), decoded_size_din)))\
    .Case(40,
        bus_r_data(Concat(Bits(28).from_py(0, 0), decoded_qos_din)))\
    .Case(44,
        bus_r_data(Concat(Bits(26).from_py(0, 0), decoded_r_id_din)))\
    .Case(48,
        bus_r_data(decoded_r_data_din))\
    .Case(52,
        bus_r_data(Concat(Bits(30).from_py(0, 0), decoded_r_resp_din)))\
    .Case(56,
        bus_r_data(Concat(Bits(31).from_py(0, 0), decoded_r_last_din)))\
    .Case(60,
        bus_r_data(Concat(Bits(26).from_py(0, 0), decoded_b_id_din)))\
    .Case(64,
        bus_r_data(Concat(Bits(30).from_py(0, 0), decoded_b_resp_din)))\
    .Case(68,
        bus_r_data(decoded_w_data_din))\
    .Case(72,
        bus_r_data(Concat(Bits(31).from_py(0, 0), decoded_w_last_din)))\
    .Case(76,
        bus_r_data(Concat(Bits(24).from_py(0, 0), decoded_w_strb_din)))\
    .Case(80,
        bus_r_data(Concat(Bits(22).from_py(0, 0), decoded_hs_din)))\
    .Default(
        bus_r_data(None))

If(clk._onRisingEdge(),
    w_strb(w_strb_next),
    w_last(w_last_next),
    w_data(w_data_next),
    size(size_next),
    r_resp(r_resp_next),
    r_last(r_last_next),
    r_id(r_id_next),
    r_data(r_data_next),
    qos(qos_next),
    prot(prot_next),
    lock(lock_next),
    len(len_next),
    cache(cache_next),
    burst(burst_next),
    b_resp(b_resp_next),
    b_id(b_id_next),
    ar_aw_w_id(ar_aw_w_id_next),
    addr(addr_next)
)

If(clk._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0),
        st(state_t.ready),
        reg_cmd_vld(0),
        reg_cmd(0)
    ).Else(
        st(st_next),
        reg_cmd_vld(reg_cmd_vld_next),
        reg_cmd(reg_cmd_next)
    )
)

hwMeta.name: Concat(Concat(Concat(Concat(Concat(Concat(Concat(Concat(Concat(st._eq(state_t.wait_ar), m_axi_ar_ready), st._eq(state_t.wait_aw)), m_axi_aw_ready), m_axi_r_valid), st._eq(state_t.wait_r)), m_axi_b_valid), st._eq(state_t.wait_b)), st._eq(state_t.wait_w)), m_axi_w_ready)

st._eq(state_t.wait_aw) & m_axi_aw_ready._eq(1) | st._eq(state_t.wait_ar) & m_axi_ar_ready._eq(1) | st._eq(state_t.wait_w) & m_axi_w_ready._eq(1) | st._eq(state_t.wait_r) & m_axi_r_valid._eq(1) | st._eq(state_t.wait_b) & m_axi_b_valid._eq(1)
st._eq(state_t.wait_aw) & m_axi_aw_ready._eq(1) | st._eq(state_t.wait_ar) & m_axi_ar_ready._eq(1) | st._eq(state_t.wait_w) & m_axi_w_ready._eq(1) | st._eq(state_t.wait_r) & m_axi_r_valid._eq(1)
